data.description: Absolutely beautiful high-end 3bd/2.5ba townhome in great Greer location! Only one year old. Gorgeous honey pine LVP floors, oversize island with farmhouse, sink, decorative backsplash tiles, high ceilings, staggered cabinets, and beautiful finishes. Primary bedroom features large walk-in closet and beautiful walk-in oversized tiled shower in bath. Multiple linen closets and storage spaces throughout. Exterior features stack stone and hardy plank with craftsman style touches and an adorable, screened in porch.
